---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import styles from "./index.module.css";

const placeholderImage = "/placeholder.jpg";
---

<Layout title="AI Model Development Cycle">
  <article class={styles.projectArticle}>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class={styles.heroSection}>
      <h1 class={styles.heroTitle}>
        Revamping the AI Model Development Life Cycle
      </h1>
      <p class={styles.heroSubtitle}>
        Streamlining the AI model development process for autonomous driving
      </p>
      <div class={styles.heroImageWrapper}>
        <img src={placeholderImage} alt="Hero Image" class={styles.heroImage} />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Overview</h2>
      <p class={styles.sectionText}>
        AIMMOâ€™s AI model development workflow was fragmented and inefficient. We
        needed a centralized solution to improve team productivity and
        streamline tasks for engineers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Background -->
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Background</h2>
      <div class={styles.twoColumnLayout}>
        <div>
          <p class={styles.sectionText}>
            AI engineers struggled with inefficiencies caused by multiple
            disconnected tools, interfaces, and limited monitoring capabilities
            for AI models.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src={placeholderImage}
            alt="Background Image"
            class={styles.sectionImage}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem -->
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Problem</h2>
      <div class={styles.problemGrid}>
        <div class={styles.card}>
          <h3 class={styles.cardTitle}>Fragmented Workflow</h3>
          <p class={styles.cardText}>
            Engineers switched between tools, causing inefficiencies and
            potential errors in the development cycle.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class={styles.card}>
          <h3 class={styles.cardTitle}>Limited Visibility</h3>
          <p class={styles.cardText}>
            Lack of centralized monitoring made tracking performance and
            progress more difficult for teams.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution -->
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Solution</h2>
      <p class={styles.sectionText}>
        We developed a unified dashboard that integrates essential tools and
        real-time monitoring for the AI model development process.
      </p>
      <div class={styles.solutionImageWrapper}>
        <img
          src={placeholderImage}
          alt="Solution Image"
          class={styles.solutionImage}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Development Timeline -->
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Development Timeline</h2>
      <div class={styles.timeline}>
        <div class={styles.timelineCard}>
          <h3 class={styles.cardTitle}>Phase 1: Research & Analysis</h3>
          <p class={styles.cardText}>
            Analyzed the existing workflow, conducted user interviews, and
            identified pain points for AI engineers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class={styles.timelineCard}>
          <h3 class={styles.cardTitle}>Phase 2: Prototyping & Design</h3>
          <p class={styles.cardText}>
            Created wireframes, high-fidelity designs, and iterated based on
            real-time feedback from users.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class={styles.timelineCard}>
          <h3 class={styles.cardTitle}>Phase 3: Implementation</h3>
          <p class={styles.cardText}>
            Worked collaboratively with developers to implement the unified
            dashboard for production.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact -->
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Impact</h2>
      <p class={styles.sectionText}>
        The new unified dashboard improved productivity, reduced development
        cycle inefficiencies, and streamlined the workflow for AI engineers. It
        empowered teams with real-time insights, enhancing overall performance.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
